Definition: the streets of a city viewed as a depressed environment in which there is poverty and crime and prostitution and dereliction
Example: she tried to keep her children off the street
Synonyms: environment, noun, location, concrete_jungle, p, the, streets, of, a, city, viewed, as, depressed, in, which, there, is, poverty, and, crime, prostitution, dereliction, she, tried, to, keep, her, children, off
Category: noun.state
